                <div style="padding: 14px 28px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); text-align: center; font-size: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">Classification: ---</div>
